- content_for :title, "About"
- content_for :description, "Bookify is an open-source reference app for the PayoutPartner API. Learn how companies use it to manage and pay freelancers."

.row.justify-content-center.mt-4
  .col-md-8
    %h1.fw-bold About Bookify
    %p.lead.text-muted
      An open-source freelancer payout management app built on the
      %a{href: "https://payoutpartner.com", target: "_blank"} PayoutPartner
      API v2.

    .card.border-0.shadow-sm.my-4
      .card-body.p-4
        %h4.fw-bold What is Bookify?
        %p
          Bookify is a working reference app that demonstrates how to manage freelancers
          and process payouts using the PayoutPartner REST API. Companies use it to invite
          freelancers, create bookings for completed work, and submit payouts.
        %p.mb-0
          It's built for operators and developers who want to build their own
          freelancer payout integration. Clone it, customize it, or just read the code.

    .card.border-0.shadow-sm.my-4
      .card-body.p-4
        %h4.fw-bold How it works
        .row.g-3.mt-2
          .col-md-6
            .d-flex.align-items-start
              %span.badge.rounded-pill.bg-primary.me-3.mt-1 1
              %div
                %strong Company invites a freelancer
                %p.text-muted.small.mb-0 Enter their email — they receive a link to accept.
          .col-md-6
            .d-flex.align-items-start
              %span.badge.rounded-pill.bg-primary.me-3.mt-1 2
              %div
                %strong Freelancer verifies identity
                %p.text-muted.small.mb-0 Through PayoutPartner's secure BankID verification flow.
          .col-md-6
            .d-flex.align-items-start
              %span.badge.rounded-pill.bg-primary.me-3.mt-1 3
              %div
                %strong Company logs work and submits payouts
                %p.text-muted.small.mb-0 Create bookings with hours and rate, then submit payouts to PayoutPartner.
          .col-md-6
            .d-flex.align-items-start
              %span.badge.rounded-pill.bg-primary.me-3.mt-1 4
              %div
                %strong Company pays the invoice
                %p.text-muted.small.mb-0 PayoutPartner generates an invoice. Once paid, the freelancer receives their payout.

    .card.border-0.shadow-sm.my-4
      .card-body.p-4
        %h4.fw-bold Links
        %ul.list-unstyled.mb-0
          %li.mb-2
            %i.bi.bi-github.me-2
            %a{href: "https://github.com/skiwo/bookify-app", target: "_blank"} Source code on GitHub
          %li.mb-2
            %i.bi.bi-globe.me-2
            %a{href: "https://payoutpartner.com", target: "_blank"} PayoutPartner
          %li
            %i.bi.bi-file-code.me-2
            %a{href: "https://sandbox.core.payoutpartner.com/api-docs", target: "_blank"} PayoutPartner API v2 documentation
